  "description": "Mobile EEG dataset from 19 participants performing outdoor walking tasks along two different routes. Participants completed each route twice, with one condition involving self-paced button pressing. This dataset characterizes gait-related artifacts in mobile EEG recordings during naturalistic locomotion.",
